         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head>
            <p>Gaius Pompilius Syrus, beneficarius, served for 25 years, aged 83.</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>For others soldiers at Ptolemais see <ref type="inscription">P07900</ref>, <ref type="inscription">P20800</ref>, <ref type="inscription">P21800</ref>. </p>
            <p> 
               <foreign xml:lang="la">Beneficiarii</foreign> are usually found attached to <foreign xml:lang="la">proconsules, legati Augusti, procuratores, praefecti, aediles, tribuni legionis</foreign>, commanders of auxilia units and city troops.</p>
         </div>
         
